\id PHP FIL - Bible Iyansi
\h FILIPE
\toc3 Fil
\toc2 FILIPE
\toc1 Fil
\mt2 Un'kaan akà
\mt1 Afilipe
\imt1 Nsɛmà
\ip Bulà a Filipe là bul atàtwɛb uboo a Ɛrɔp alà kàlɔŋ Pɔl Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ, u prɔvɛnsɛ a itaan là Lɔmà u Masɛdwan. Nde kàtöŋ Ikööŋ u bul a Filipe unsà ndyaaŋ ande yà yweel. Baar bamwɛy bàtɛn naa nde kàkäl u bɔlokà ungö a mbul mbɔɔn kà Ɛfɛsɔ, nde kàkyà Sɛzarɛ a Lɔmà. Ntööm kàsöön baar a Filipe un'kaan mwɛy wun'sak ntɔɔn an'kab bun'tööm ba umbwo a Ɛpafrɔdi, itàkal naa nde ŋakwo kàkäl unsà mpay. Nde kàkwen mukapà un'kanà mukal bàlàbɔ̈ɔ̈n amu Klistɔ anà mukɔɔn abwà unsà ndɛb a an'lɔɔŋ a lor màyiywolà uboo a iköŋ aba. Nde wàmupà un'kanà akà baar a Filipo mukal bàŋàtsim unsà làkwikilà aba anà muleŋ un'tüüb aŋàbwaŋ uboo a ba, muswaŋ mbaan a làbɔ̈ɔ̈n anà dweelà isal bye ifàfà amu Yɛsu Klistɔ. Pa bàdiilà ba mukun'man, Ɛpafrɔdi, ntööm a baar a Filipo anà Tumàtɛ, un'baay a Pɔl, bàkär un'tüüb awà uboo a ntööm Pɔl anà iköŋ a baar a Filipo. Ungö nde wàmusà baar a Filipo ngwalàngwal unsà ikyɛɛŋ akà baar bàkɔ̈ɔ̈n làbɔ̈ɔ̈n akà Làsaŋ a ndandaa. Nde wàmukyäänà baar a Filipo ntɔn ba bàläb nkääl ande, muler mper a isin a mɔ̈ɔ̈ a iklistɔ: ikaswaŋà naa mubulà balàbal a Yɛsu Klistɔ. Kutsü, un'kaan wà mupà un'kanà, an'tɔɔn anà mbɔr. Un'kaan awà bàbeelà naa « un'kaan a un'sak » ntɔn ntsü anà ntsü ikasaamà ndaa awa. Un'sak awà wà unsà làbɔ̈ɔ̈n amu Klistɔ.
\c 1
\s1 Mbɔr
\p 
\v 1 Pɔl anà Tumàtɛ, asyääl a Klistɔ Yɛsu.
\p Anà aŋin'kyɛɛl banswà abà amu Klistɔ Yɛsu u Filipe anà aseey anà asadidi:
\v 2 Wɛy Taaràbi Nzam anà Mwol Yɛsu Klistɔ bàlapɛ kab a ngway anà duu.
\s1 An'tɔɔn anà ngyamàkà
\p 
\v 3 Mɛ in'fàfuur an'tɔɔn akà Nzam amɛ u mbalà yanswà in'fàyɔbà mɛ bɛ,
\v 4 taaŋ lanswà uboo a ngyamàkà amɛ ntɔn bɛ banswà, mɛ in'fàyɔn anki muyamà unsà un'sak,
\v 5 ntɔn kab làfàwal bɛ unsà Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ, sɛmà ilä atàtwɛb tii ŋàbà.
\v 6 Wɛɛ mɛ an'sà làkyän naa mbuur kàsɛmà amu bɛ isal aŋàbwaŋ aki akyer asàlab ntsüü a kya tii ilä usàyà Klistɔ Yɛsu.
\v 7 Ya yà balàbal naa mɛ in'käl anà an'kyän a tub amà akà bɛ banswà, ntɔn bɛ làbà u mpem amɛ, bɛ baar làfàwal kab uboo a kab a ngway alà ban'pɛ, itàkal apanà in'wà mɛ u bɔlokà itàkal mpal in'fànwään mɛ Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ anà in'fàtɛɛl mɛ la imbäl.
\v 8 Inye, Nzam wà mbäl amɛ naa mɛ in'fàkwen bɛ banswà mbɔɔn unsà ukwen a Klistɔ Yɛsu.
\p 
\v 9 Waa mɛ in'fàyamà abà: wɛy ukwen abɛ bàlalà muyɛl mbɔɔn unsà ngyööb anà nsɔ̈ɔ̈l yanswà,
\v 10 ntɔn bɛ làyöb musɔɔl indiir a ndöŋ. Abun, bɛ làsàkal bàŋàpɔŋà anà ukɔɔn an'pɛl kà ilä a Klistɔ.
\v 11 Bɛ làsàkal bàŋàyɔl a imbɛŋ a balàbal kyan'fà akà Klistɔ Yɛsu ntɔn bi, unsà làkoo anà nsyäŋà a Nzam.
\s1 Klistɔ wà mɔ̈ɔ̈
\p 
\v 12 Atɔŋ, mɛ in'kwen naa bɛ làyɔb: indiir byan'yeel, byàpɛ mbwo akà Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ mukyà usà.
\v 13 Kyakin, u làpaŋ a kuvernɔ̈ɔ̈r, itàkal u mper yanswà, bàkyàyöb naa mɛ in'wà u bɔlokà ntɔn Klistɔ,
\v 14 anà atɔŋ mbɔɔn bàkyàwal ngwal unsà Mwol u mbwo a bɔlokà amɛ, ba bàfàkwɛy kyääl mulɔŋ Ndaa a Nzam ukɔɔn bɔɔmà.
\p 
\v 15 Yà ndandaa, baar amwɛy bàfàkyer unsà un'köl anà isür, wɛɛ bumwɛy bàfàlɔŋ Klistɔ unsà an'kyän aŋàbwaŋ.
\v 16 Baar abà bàkyer unsà ukwen, ntɔn ba bàkyàyöb naa isal amɛ apà kyàmunwään Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ.
\v 17 Wɛɛ baar bàfàkyään Klistɔ unsà isür, an'kyän aba man'be, ba bàkwen mukwɛy mpay aŋàsöönà u bɔlokà amɛ.
\p 
\v 18 Wɛɛ, undiir watɛy! Undiir awà ndöŋ wà naa u mbwo yanswà, itàkal unsà an'kyän an'be itàkal unsà ndandaa, bàmukyäänà Klistɔ. Waa mɛ an'man un'sak ntɔn ya. Inye, mɛ in'yàlalà muman un'sak ntɔn ya.
\v 19 Ntɔn mɛ in'kyàyöb naa yayin yanswà isàkal ntɔn ngweel a mɔ̈ɔ̈ amɛ, u mbwo a ngyamàkà abɛ anà mbaay a Dweelà a Klistɔ Yɛsu.
\v 20 Undiir indilà mɛ anà in'saa mɛ làkyän u mpem amɛ wanswà, wà naa akà undiir mwɛy ukɔ̈ɔ̈n an'mɛɛy nswɛn, wɛɛ Klistɔ uwɛl làkoo u ndür amɛ, apanà anà utaaŋ lanswà, unsà kam lanswà, itàkal u mbwo a mɔ̈ɔ̈ amɛ, itàkal u mbwo a ukwà amɛ.
\v 21 Ntɔn mɛ, mɔ̈ɔ̈ wà Klistɔ, ukwà bà bweel.
\v 22 Wɛɛ isàkal naa ukal anà mɔ̈ɔ̈ u mɛɛn mà, yan'pà mbwo mutwey mbɛŋ unsà isal amɛ, mɛ in'yöb anki naa mɛ ininà in'sɔɔl.
\v 23 Ndaa yweel yan'naanà mper anà mper: mɛ in'we anà ngyal mukyà anà mukal anà Klistɔ, ntɔn ya yan'söön ubwaŋ,
\v 24 wɛɛ yan'söön ndöŋ mbɔɔn mukal u mɛɛn pà ntɔn bɛ.
\v 25 Apan sye, mɛ an'sà kam, mɛ in'kyàyöb naa mɛ in'kyer ayàlam anà in'yàlalà mukal tsütsü apà bɛ banswà ntɔn mukàlabay mukyà usà anà muman un'sak a làkwikilà abɛ.
\v 26 Abun, umpal in'yàfurà mɛ apà bɛ, ngaal abɛ amu Klistɔ Yɛsu ifàsöönà.
\s1 Ukɔɔn akwamà unsà ngwiy
\p 
\v 27 Wɛɛ itàkal kà aben, làsyen mɔ̈ɔ̈ abɛ asànaa làkwen Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ a Klistɔ, ntɔn, isàkal naa mɛ amàyàlaler, itàkal naa mɛ in'yi anki, mɛ in'wem làsaŋ naa bɛ lan'tsim unsà dweelà làmwɛy la, làbàmunwaan mbwo mwɛy unsà mpem mwɛy ntɔn làkwikilà amu Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ.
\v 28 Twon lan'man ayiiŋ abɛ bɔɔmà: kya isakal idiim ntɔn mbweel aba anà ngweel a mɔ̈ɔ̈ abɛ. Ya yanswà yan'fà akà Nzam.
\v 29 Ntɔn Klistɔ, nde kàlapɛ kab a ngway kà nà mukun'sà làkwikilà mpɛl anki, wɛɛ muman an'kaal sye ntɔn nde.
\v 30 Apanà, bɛ làbàmunwaan ngwiy nsil ya lan'mɛn bɛ munwaan anà ifàkamwanà mɛ asànaa làyöb bɛ.
\c 2
\s1 Làbɔ̈ɔ̈n a Klistɔ
\p 
\v 1 Abun, isàkal naa un'tüüb abɛ anà Klistɔ afàlapà ngwal, ndɛɛl unsà ukwen ande, anà un'tüüb anà nde u mbwo a Dweelà, ngyɛb anà ubwaŋ uboo a bɛ,
\v 2 apan, làyööl mpem amɛ a un'sak mbɔɔn mukal mun mwɛy, ukwen mwɛy, an'kyän an'mwɛy anà un'tüüb mwɛy.
\v 3 Twon làkyer akà undiir mwɛy unsà isür, itàkal unsà làkoo làkɔ̈ɔ̈n ndöŋ, wɛɛ, anà làbɔ̈ɔ̈n, lawɛl atɔŋ asànaa ba ban'söön bɛ ŋakwo.
\v 4 Wɛy mbuur ukɔ̈ɔ̈n aler ndaa ande ŋakwo mpɛl, wɛɛ nde uler sye ndaa a baar bumwɛy.
\v 5 Làkäl anà ifà a tub aki amu bɛ, ifà kyàkäl amu Yɛsu Klistɔ:
\q1 
\v 6 Nde mbuur kàkäl asànaa Nzam,
\q1 nde kàwɛl anki wa asànaa undiir agyɔɔr mukal balàbal anà Nzam.
\q1 
\v 7 Wɛɛ nde kàkɔɔb ya yanswà kàkäl nde ayà,
\q1 waa kàbulà asànaa un'sɔ,
\q1 asànaa baar,
\q1 ntabwey ande asànaa yà mbuur,
\q1 
\v 8 nde kàtyeey nde ŋakwo anà kàswɛŋ unkyeey
\q1 tii kà ukwà, itàkal ukwà a kulunsi.
\q1 
\v 9 Kyakin Nzam kun'sɛn nde u dudu u mbwo a kab a ngway
\q1 anà kun'pɛ nde ikɔb kyan'söön ikɔb byanswà,
\v 10 ntɔn naa kà ikɔb a Yɛsu,
\q1 an'bwaaŋ manswà màbü an'köm
\q1 u du, u mɛɛn anà ungyɛl a mɛɛn,
\v 11 anà ndaa yanswà yàtɛ imbäl naa:
\q1 « Yɛsu Klistɔ wà Mwol! »
\q1 ntɔn làkoo a Taa Nzam.
\s1 An'pɛɛlà u mɛɛn
\p 
\v 12 Kyakin, nkween amɛ, bɛ baar làfàkal aŋunkyeey taaŋ lanswà, làkäl abun kà nà u mii amɛ mpel anki, wɛɛ aŋàsöönà apanà mpa in'wà mɛ paa! Làsyääl ngweel a mɔ̈ɔ̈ abɛ unsà bɔɔmà anà matɛɛr,
\v 13 ntɔn wà Nzam afàsal uboo a bɛ anà afàlapà ngyal mukwen anà mukyer ndaa yanswà asànaa kàlɔ̈n nde unsà ukwen ande.
\p 
\v 14 Làkyer indiir byanswà ukɔɔn in'ŋün anà mbaaŋ,
\v 15 ntɔn bɛ làkɔɔn akal anà pɛl, làkäl ankɔr anà bàŋàpɔŋà, baan a Nzam bàkɔ̈ɔ̈n ube uboo a baar abɛ bà mɛɛn mà abye anà an'kyän an'be. Uboo aba bɛ làbàmupà in'ŋyäŋ asànaa ndem a mbaa u mɛɛn
\v 16 ntɔn bɛ lamɛɛy ndaa a mɔ̈ɔ̈. Abun, bɛ làsàkal ngaal amɛ kà ilä usàyà Klistɔ, ntɔn kà abunàbun anki mɛ kàsäl anà kàmɛn ntaan.
\p 
\v 17 Wɛɛ, itàkal naa mɛ an'tyaŋà asànaa man itàkal may udu a ibɔɔn anà isal a làkwikilà abɛ, mɛ in'wà unsà un'sak anà musaŋ anà bɛ banswà.
\v 18 Wɛɛ itàkal bɛ sye, làkal kà un'sak mutüüb anà mɛ.
\s1 Tumàtɛ anà Ɛpafrɔdit
\p 
\v 19 Amu Mwol Yɛsu, mɛ in'wɛ anà làkyän mukàlatööm Tumàtɛ itaan a mbɔɔn tɛy, ntɔn mɛ in'wɛl ndɛɛl unsà làsaŋ abɛ uyan'twääl nde.
\v 20 Nà nde mpɛl afàkab an'kyän anà mɛ, anà afàman mpay ndandaa ntɔn ubwaŋ abɛ.
\v 21 Ntɔn baar banswà bàfàleŋ ubwaŋ aba ŋakwo, wɛɛ kà bà Yɛsu Klistɔ anki.
\v 22 Kyekà, bɛ làkyàyöb naa Tumàtɛ kàkyàswaŋ lää ande: asànaa mwan anà taarànde, nde kàbääb anà mɛ unsà isal a Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ.
\v 23 Kyakin mɛ in'we anà làkyän mukàlatööm awà umpal in'yàyöb mɛ naa ndaa amɛ yan'tsü aben.
\v 24 Mɛ in'wɛ anà làkyän unsà Mwol naa mɛ ŋakwo in'kyer ayàlaler itaan a mbɔɔn tɛy.
\v 25 Wɛɛ apanà, mɛ in'manà naa yà mfun naa mɛ alàtööm un'tɔŋ amɛ Ɛpafrɔdit, mbuur ifàsal bi anà ifànwaan bi ità anà nde, mbuur awà lan'tööm bɛ mukambay unsà indiir kàkäl mɛ abyà mfun,
\v 26 ntɔn nde kàkäl anà ngyal mbɔɔn mufàlaman bɛ banswà anà nde kàmɛnà mpay mbɔɔn u mpem ntɔn làwem bɛ làsaŋ a ukyal ande.
\v 27 Inye, nde kàkäl anà ukyal, tsütsü mukwà, wɛɛ Nzam kun'wem ngyɛb, kà nde mpɛl anki, wɛɛ mɛ sye, ntɔn mɛ mukɔɔn aman ngyɛb udu a ngyɛb.
\v 28 Lalan mɛ an'kyer làgyägyä mufàlatööm awà, umpal làyuman bɛ, bɛ làkäl unsà un'sak, anà mɛ in'kɔ̈ɔ̈n akal anà ngyɛb mbɔɔn.
\v 29 Lun'wɛl unsà un'sak wanswà unsà Mwol anà lakömà baar a tub abà.
\v 30 Ntɔn nde kàkyer alàkwà ntɔn isal a Klistɔ: nde kàsi mɔ̈ɔ̈ ande unsà igɔnsà ntɔn mukan'pà mbaay làlàkwo bɛ ŋakwo mukan'pà.
\c 3
\s1 Balàbal u mii a Nzam
\p 
\v 1 Mumay, atɔŋ amɛ, làkäl kà un'sak unsà Mwol. Kà mpay anki akà mɛ mufuur indiir akwà kàsön mɛ, anà bya byà ubwaŋ ntɔn bɛ.
\v 2 Làkäl kà igyɛɛŋ akà mbwà, akà baar a isal abɛ anà akà bàŋàkyɛy a loor.
\v 3 Wɛɛ kiin a baar bàkyɛy bà bi, ntɔn bi ifàsyääl Nzam unsà Dweelà, bi ibye anà ngaal mukal amu Klistɔ Yɛsu, wɛɛ kà uboo a ndür abi ŋakwo anki,
\v 4 itàkal naa mɛ ŋakwo an'kwo in'si mpem amɛ u ndür. Isàkal naa mbuur asin akwen mupà mpem ande amu nde ŋakwo, mɛ, mɛ an'kwo in'kyer yàŋasöönà.
\v 5 Ntɔn mɛ ban'kyɛy kà ilä kyànaan ungö a mböör amɛ. Mɛ in'wà un'nsi Isàlɛl, u mbil a Bɛnsàmɛn, Un'nsi Ebɛlyɔ mwan a Bebɛlyɔ, umfarisi unsà un'kɔɔn,
\v 6 ntɔn un'kanà, mɛ kàmɛɛyà Ikööŋ nkwaaŋ. Ntɔn balàbal alà uboo a un'kɔɔn, akà pɛl mwɛy latɛy amu mɛ.
\v 7 Wɛɛ indiir abi byanswà byakäl bweel ntɔn mɛ, apanà mɛ bya in'manà asanaa bwà ntɔn Klistɔ.
\v 8 Inye, undiir wanswà mɛ in'kamanà asànaa wà bunàbun musi a ubwaŋ abà: ngyööb a Klistɔ Yɛsu, Mwol amɛ. Ntɔn nde, indiir byanswà byà bwà anà in'fàman bya asànaa nkayal, ntɔn muwal bweel: Klistɔ
\v 9 anà mumɛnà amu nde, ukɔɔn akal anà balàbal amɛ lan'fà unsà un'kɔɔn, wɛɛ lan'fà unsà làkwikilà amu Klistɔ, balàbal lan'fà akà Nzam u mbwo a làkwikilà.
\v 10 Mɛ in'kwen muyöb Klistɔ, ngwal a ngwiiyà ande anà un'tüüb u mpay ande, mubulà asànaa nde unsà ukwà ande,
\v 11 ntɔn mutol, kya mbwo isàkal, u ngwiiyà a akü.
\s1 Ntiin ntɔn muwal iböŋ
\p 
\v 12 Iswaŋà anki naa mɛ kàkyàwal indiir abi byanswà, itàkal naa mɛ kàkyàkwo. Wɛɛ mɛ in'wàmulab ntiin amɛ ntɔn mɛ in'wɛl bya, ntɔn mɛ ŋakwo sye Yɛsu kàkyan'wal.
\v 13 Atɔŋ, mɛ in'sii naa mɛ ŋàtàwal anki akà undiir mwɛy. Wɛɛ mɛ in'fàkyer undiir mwɛy mpɛl: mudiimà indiir abyà ungö anà mudüül indiir abyà kusà.
\v 14 Abun, mɛ in'wà mukaamà ntiin tii u ntsüü, ntɔn mɛ in'wɛl mban a mbeel a Nzam fà du u mbwo a Klistɔ Yɛsu.
\v 15 Bi banswà, baar aŋàtsim unsà Dweelà, ifàyweer abun. Apan sye, isàkal naa bɛ làwe anà undiir asin làyweerà, Nzam akyer ayàlamɛɛy wa.
\v 16 Itàkal kà aben, kà ikal ban'kɔlà bi ki, wɛy bi ilalà mukyà mbwo mwɛy.
\v 17 Atɔŋ, bɛ banswà làläb mbaan amɛ, anà làsi iler abɛ akà baar bàfàlab mbaan ayi.
\v 18 Ntɔn, bàmbɔɔn, u mbwo a nkääl aba, bà ayiiŋ a kulunsi a Klistɔ, asànaa in'fàtɛn mɛ a bɛ mbalà mbɔɔn anà in'fàfuur mɛ apanà anà nsaaŋ u mii:
\v 19 ntsüü aba isàkal ukwà, nzam aba wà an'bäl aba, làkoo aba ba bàfàsà unsà indiir a nswɛn aba, an'kyän aba mà unsà indiir a mɛɛn.
\v 20 Wɛɛ akà bi, bi ibà baar a du, ntsü uyàfà Un'tswää a mɔ̈ɔ̈ abi ikadilà bi, Mwol Yɛsu Klistɔ.
\v 21 Apan, nde asàsɔɔm ndür abi yà nswɛn ntɔn mubuul ya asànaa ndür ande yà làkoo, u mbwo a ngwal ande ifun'pà mbwo musà indiir byanswà ungyɛl a ikɔ̈b ande.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Abwɛy, atɔŋ amɛ bà nkween, mɛ in'we anà ngyal mbɔɔn mukàlaman! Bɛ làbà un'sak anà mbaan amɛ! Abun, atɔŋ amɛ, làtsim ubɔɔ a mɔ̈ɔ̈ abɛ anà Mwol.
\s1 Ndɛɛl
\p 
\v 2 Mɛ an'lɛɛl Ivodi anà mɛ an'lɛɛl Sɛntisha mukal an'kyän an'mwɛy unsà Mwol.
\v 3 Anà ngye sye, un'baay amɛ wàndandaa, mɛ amalɔm mukabay, ntɔn ba bànwään mbwo mwɛy anà mɛ ntɔn Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ, sye, anà Klɛma anà abaay amɛ bumwɛy, ikɔb aba byà ubɔɔ a un'kaan a mɔ̈ɔ̈.
\v 4 Taaŋ lanswà, làkäl kà un'sak unsà Mwol. Mɛ an'fàfuur: làkäl kà un'sak!
\v 5 Wɛy baar banswà bàyöb ubwaŋ angye. Mwol wà tsütsü.
\v 6 Twon lan'kyɛɛr a bunàbun, wɛɛ unsà ipöl kyanswà, u mbwo a ngyamàkà anà u mbwo a ndɔ̈ɔ̈m anà an'tɔɔn, làswɛŋ ngyal abɛ akà Nzam.
\v 7 Abun, duu a Nzam alà lan'lyaaŋ un'yɛnà wanswà, làyàkaar mpem abɛ anà an'kyän abɛ amu Klistɔ Yɛsu.
\v 8 Atɔŋ, mumay, làsi an'kyän abɛ unsà indiir a ndandaa, byà ibyääl, byàbalàbal, byàŋàpɔŋà, byà ukwen, byàŋàsyäŋà, byàŋàbwaŋ, anà byàlàkoo.
\v 9 Indiir làlɔŋàkà bɛ, làwɛl bɛ anà làwem bɛ akà mɛ, làsyääl bya. Waa Nzam a duu uyàkal anà bɛ.
\s1 Pɔl kan'fuur an'tɔɔn akà Afilipo
\p 
\v 10 Mɛ kàmɛn un'sak mbɔɔn unsà Mwol ntɔn làfàsà bɛ an'kyän abɛ amu mɛ: Inye, bɛ làkäl anà an'kyän amà, wɛɛ bɛ làkäl anki anà ipöl muswaŋ ma.
\v 11 Mɛ in'tɛɛnà anki abwɛy naa ntɔn mɛ an'kwà nkyääŋ a indiir, ntɔn mɛ kàlɔŋàkà mukal anà un'sak a indiir in'wà mɛ abyà.
\v 12 Mɛ in'kyàyöb mukal u làmbwà anà mukal unsà indiir mbɔɔn. Mɛ kàlɔŋàkà mukal aŋàyuur anà mukal u ngyal, mukal unsà indiir mbɔɔn asànaa u ngyal.
\v 13 Mɛ an'kwo mukyer indiir byanswa amu mbuur afan'pà ngwal.
\v 14 Apan sye, bɛ làkyer ubwaŋ muwal kab unsà mpay amɛ.
\v 15 Bɛ làkyàyöb, bɛ, Afilipo: u nsɛmà a Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ, umpal kàlwomà mɛ u Masɛdwan, akà Ikööŋ imwɛy kyan'si anki u kab, nà bɛ mpɛl.
\v 16 Ntɔn mpal kàkäl mɛ u Tɛsalɔnikà, mbalà mbɔɔn bɛ lan'tööm indiir kàkäl mɛ abyà mfun.
\v 17 Ikaswaŋà anki naa mɛ in'wàmuleŋ kab, wɛɛ mɛ in'kaleŋà naa bweel abɛ bàbɛy.
\v 18 Abun, mɛ an'kyey naa mɛ kàkyàwal indiir byanswà lan'tööm bɛ. Bya byan'söön mbɔɔn. Apanà mɛ an'yɔl a un'sak ntɔn Epafrɔdit kàman'twääl nde an'kab abɛ: may a usɔŋ aŋàbwaŋ, ibɔɔn kan'kyey Nzam anà kya kyàmupà un'sak.
\v 19 Nzam amɛ akyer ayàkölà ngyal abɛ, asànaa awà un'naaŋ ande unsà làkoo amu Klistɔ Yɛsu.
\v 20 Wɛy làkoo làkäl akà Taaràbi Nzam u mbul a in'tye. Yà abwɛy.
\s1 Mbɔr a ntsüü
\p 
\v 21 Làpɛ mbɔr akà ŋin'kyɛɛl wanswà amu Klistɔ Yɛsu. Atɔŋ abà anà mɛ bàmalatööm mbɔr.
\v 22 Aŋin'kyɛɛl banswà bàmàlapà mbɔr, sin sin baar a ndwà a Sɛzar.
\v 23 Wɛy kab a ngway a Mwol Yɛsu Klistɔ làkäl anà dweelà abɛ.
